{"tid":744760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國旗觀眾席飄揚蓋克羅地亞　央視大讚感動　網民：告訴世界我們早已五星了","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T13:21:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":519,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"c6619432d347d2a79b71bd4ec8166d6e110f0dd9","tid":744760,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180716/s00006/52c35786ac036d4bfdadad974998804c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180716%2Fs00006%2F52c35786ac036d4bfdadad974998804c.jpg&h=3308f26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國和克羅地亞的隊伍周日晚在球場內表演了一場精采絕倫的比賽，全球目光都停留在莫斯科。有中國球迷趁着兩國球員比併之際，在觀眾席揚起中國國旗，甚至掩蓋着克羅地亞的國旗。央視網在微博大讚該球迷的行為令人感動，亦有網民表示：「告訴世界我們早已五星。」<br />\n<br />\n比賽開始了33分鐘，兩隊互入一球，正在緊張之際。中國網民「大鍋只是喝醉」發現在觀眾席上出現了一面國旗，便影相放上網分享，隨即獲得多人讚好轉發。<br />\n<br />\n有在現場觀看比賽的網民表示，當時其實很多人都帶了國旗到場，他自己也披着國旗觀賽。不少網民都感慨：「國足可能遲到」、「起碼國旗到了啊！」、「提前四年為中國隊加油」，甚至有人表示：「這是要告訴世界中國早就已經五星 （一星代表球隊贏一次世界盃）了。」<br />\n<br />\n央視網亦發文讚賞該球迷：「明知不可而為之，明知渺茫仍拼之，明知&hellip;&hellip;還是心存希望！這一幕才令人感動，不是嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n亦有很多網民認為很丟臉，直指該行為是諷刺國足，不過旋即被其他網民斥責不愛國，是「崇洋媚外的惡蟲」，「世界杯又不是只有球隊參加，球迷也是重要組成部分。人家打着旗子來看球不行嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/153832_5e4fb8069b2a673d26051cd4fa526cb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F153832_5e4fb8069b2a673d26051cd4fa526cb8.png&h=1ce85153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180716/s00006/1531724460211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180716%2Fs00006%2F1531724460211&d=Hsg6bBXkDCZF%2F1K4r0b0Jb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9e9c6b0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180716%2Fs00006%2F1531724460211&h=88adcf07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180716/s00006/1531724460211</a>"},{"pid":"a54a0252e7b13b49e7125adebf5119d34831b7c2","tid":744760,"uid":26976,"like":406,"dislike":2,"score":404,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"你要打飛機咪拎嚟包住碌鳩打囉<br />\n做乜遮住人地支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbba26ca629866909e0fdd641598dcdfa3e7a786","tid":744760,"uid":56401,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"quote":{"pid":"a54a0252e7b13b49e7125adebf5119d34831b7c2","tid":744760,"uid":26976,"like":406,"dislike":2,"score":404,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"你要打飛機咪拎嚟包住碌鳩打囉<br />\n做乜遮住人地支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"支那人<br />\n你感意外嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8a9c6b76e54dd7dabe98e51dc0d74ca8f6dfc5","tid":744760,"uid":121911,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"真正既睇到打曬冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b1311d542759036432b0d967f6e90e9be3ee3","tid":744760,"uid":37820,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"班中國人究竟係咩邏輯<br />\n世界盃又同佢冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴埋嚟做乜"},{"pid":"51c94d4cf86a07a95885825397ff32037187719f","tid":744760,"uid":65061,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"0e8e76f2e8dce2afb13e8afd228fb1822c6207c9","tid":744760,"uid":50540,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"quote":{"pid":"c6619432d347d2a79b71bd4ec8166d6e110f0dd9","tid":744760,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt